    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 (VAD hemolysis, MRL 5) is accepted as a complete assessment record. Seven of thirteen factors were formally assessed; six factors were flagged as not-assessed epistemic gaps consistent with MRL 5 requirements. All assessed factors show achieved levels below required levels, confirming the Not Accepted submission decision. The package is accepted as a valid credibility evidence record for regulatory review purposes. Note: provenance records for validation results at operating points 3 and 4 do not carry structured activity links; the generating experiments were described narratively in the test report but the activity identifiers were not captured in the structured evidence package.",
